    <item>
      <title>扎克伯格访问白宫讨论美国科技领导力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/zuckerberg-visits-white-house-to-discuss-us-tech-leadership</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Meta Platforms Inc. 的发言人安迪·斯通 (Andy Stone) 在 X 上的一篇帖子中表示，该公司首席执行官马克·扎克伯格周四访问了白宫，讨论公司如何支持特朗普政府加强美国科技领导地位的努力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/zuckerberg-visits-white-house-to-discuss-us-tech-leadership</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 22:52:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝森特在“完全认同”马斯克的同时，也预测一切将恢复正常</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bessent-projects-normalcy-while-completely-aligned-with-musk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯科特·贝森特担任财政部长仅两周，就经历了许多动荡。该部门成为埃隆·马斯克打击联邦支出的打击目标——引发贝森特办公室外的抗议——投资者对唐纳德·特朗普总统不可预测的贸易政策感到不安。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/bessent-projects-normalcy-while-completely-aligned-with-musk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 22:50:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的世界自由金融计划创建“战略”代币储备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-s-world-liberty-financial-plans-to-create-strategic-token-reserve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统的 DeFi 项目 World Liberty Financial 的联合创始人蔡斯·赫罗 (Chase Herro) 表示，该平台计划利用购买的代币创建“战略储备”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-s-world-liberty-financial-plans-to-create-strategic-token-reserve</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 22:50:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普与中国的贸易战波及香港</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/hong-kong-gets-swept-up-in-trump-s-trade-war-with-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普发起的新贸易战进一步模糊了香港和北京之间的界限，有可能削弱香港作为全球金融中心的主要卖点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/hong-kong-gets-swept-up-in-trump-s-trade-war-with-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝森特表示，马斯克的 DOGE 团队不允许“修修补补”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-02-06/for-musk-s-doge-team-no-tinkering-allowed-bessent-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[这是华盛顿版，一份关于首都金钱、权力和政治的新闻通讯。今天，白宫和政治记者 Gregory Korte 概述了财政部长 Scott Bessent 如何与 Elon Musk 的 DOGE 团队合作。请在此处注册并关注我们 @bpolitics。请在此处向我们的编辑发送电子邮件。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2025-02-06/for-musk-s-doge-team-no-tinkering-allowed-bessent-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 21:42:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普支持国际刑事法院对加沙地带实施制裁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-backs-international-criminal-court-sanctions-amid-gaza-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统批准对调查美国及其盟友的国际刑事法院官员实施制裁，重启其第一任期内的一项政策，针对该组织，他称其对美国主权构成威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-backs-international-criminal-court-sanctions-amid-gaza-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 21:29:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中情局新招募人员名单可能被对手利用数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/cia-list-of-new-recruits-risks-adversaries-exploiting-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在唐纳德·特朗普总统寻求削减联邦工作人员规模之际，美国中央情报局为遵守行政命令，将新招募的人员名单放在一封非机密电子邮件中发送给白宫，此举可能为额外的国家安全风险打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/cia-list-of-new-recruits-risks-adversaries-exploiting-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 21:07:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿根廷国会支持米莱暂停初选投票的请求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/argentina-lower-house-backs-milei-s-bid-to-suspend-primary-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷国会众议院投票决定暂停今年中期选举的初选，这为总统哈维尔·米莱领导的政党扩大其在立法机构中的影响力提供了助力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/argentina-lower-house-backs-milei-s-bid-to-suspend-primary-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 20:59:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将在税收法案中寻求终止附带权益并扩大 SALT</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-will-seek-to-end-carried-interest-expand-salt-in-tax-bill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统唐纳德·特朗普在与共和党议员的会议上概述了他的税收优先事项，包括终止私募股权基金经理使用的附带权益税收减免，并扩大州和地方税收减免。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-will-seek-to-end-carried-interest-expand-salt-in-tax-bill</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 18:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普会见美国钢铁公司首席执行官，新日铁希望挽救交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-to-meet-us-steel-ceo-as-nippon-steel-holds-out-deal-hope</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情官员透露，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普周四在白宫会见了美国钢铁公司首席执行官戴夫·伯里特，而此时人们对该公司的命运存有疑问。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-06/trump-to-meet-us-steel-ceo-as-nippon-steel-holds-out-deal-hope</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 06 Feb 2025 17:06:04 GMT</pubDate>
